518
00:40:28,326 --> 00:40:29,794
because she's the one Daoming Si loves.

519
00:40:30,595 --> 00:40:31,996
I don't have the right to blame her.

520
00:40:33,498 --> 00:40:34,599
I just don't understand.

521
00:40:35,266 --> 00:40:36,935
She told me she's leaving Taiwan.

522
00:40:37,368 --> 00:40:39,070
Why is she getting engaged
to Daoming Si today?

523
00:40:39,137 --> 00:40:41,506
She really meant to leave Taiwan.

524
00:40:42,407 --> 00:40:44,976
She didn't get to leave for a reason.

525
00:40:47,078 --> 00:40:47,979
Sha.

526
00:40:48,413 --> 00:40:49,347
What is the reason?

527
00:40:49,714 --> 00:40:50,715
It's...

528
00:40:53,451 --> 00:40:55,019
Tell us, Sha.

529
00:40:57,255 --> 00:40:58,323
I met her before.

530
00:40:59,324 --> 00:41:00,558
I met that Yesha before.

531
00:41:01,893 --> 00:41:02,961
What's going on?

532
00:41:03,928 --> 00:41:05,430
When I saw the news earlier,

533
00:41:05,496 --> 00:41:07,699
