looked familiar.

534
00:41:08,700 --> 00:41:10,101
I finally remember now.

535
00:41:10,969 --> 00:41:14,739
Before meeting Ah Si, she told me
she studied in Yingde University

536
00:41:14,806 --> 00:41:16,407
and she kept asking
for information about us.

537
00:41:19,010 --> 00:41:20,511
She must have approached me intentionally.

538
00:41:21,746 --> 00:41:23,381
Stop making assumptions.

539
00:41:23,915 --> 00:41:25,783
Yesha is a princess.

540
00:41:25,850 --> 00:41:27,452
Why would she approach you intentionally?

541
00:41:29,020 --> 00:41:30,621
She must have wanted to help Ah Xing

542
00:41:30,688 --> 00:41:31,856
get back his memories.

543
00:41:32,357 --> 00:41:33,791
Then why did she approach Shancai?

544
00:41:33,858 --> 00:41:34,892
She...

545
00:41:34,959 --> 00:41:35,860
Tell me.

546
00:41:37,161 --> 00:41:38,329
I don't know.

547
00:41:38,396 --> 00:41:40,465
Anyway, I'm sure Yesha
is not that kind of person.

548
00:41:41,466 --> 00:41:43,034
The truth is in front of us.

549
00:41:43,701 --> 00:41:45,169
She really did lie to Shancai.

550
00:41:45,236 --> 00:41:46,304
She...

551
00:41:46,371 --> 00:41:47,572
Sha is right.

552
00:41:48,139 --> 00:41:49,941
The Yesha that I know
is not that kind of person.

553
00:41:50,475 --> 00:41:51,476
That's right.

554
00:41:52,143 --> 00:41:53,811
It's not that simple.

555
00:41:54,212 --> 00:41:55,880
Think about it.

556
00:41:56,748 --> 00:41:58,216
Based on Yesha's status,

557
00:41:58,282 --> 00:42:01,486
isn't it easy to marry
a simple-minded person like Ah Xing?

558
00:42:01,919 --> 00:42:05,289
Why would she waste her efforts
just to trick Shancai?

559
00:42:06,290 --> 00:42:07,291
That's right.

560
00:42:08,493 --> 00:42:10,094
She's a princess from Bhutan.

561
00:42:12,964 --> 00:42:14,899
The Empress Dowager
surely wouldn't miss the opportunity

562
00:42:15,566 --> 00:42:17,201
to become a royal family in-law.

563
00:42:19,170 --> 00:42:20,638
She's literally the empress dowager now.

564
00:42:29,680 --> 00:42:31,783
What's the matter, Yesha?

565
00:42:32,483 --> 00:42:34,018
Are you all right?

566
00:42:34,752 --> 00:42:35,987
I'm fine.

567
00:42:36,454 --> 00:42:38,556
I just hate answering
those boring questions.

568
00:42:39,323 --> 00:42:41,859
Don't mind me. Go and greet the press.

569
00:42:41,926 --> 00:42:44,629
No, I want to stay here with you.

570
00:42:45,763 --> 00:42:46,964
I'm fine, really.

571
00:42:49,434 --> 00:42:51,903
It's awkward to deal with the press.
I don't want to go.

572
00:42:55,406 --> 00:42:57,108
You're the successor
of Daoming Corporation.

573
00:42:57,708 --> 00:42:59,710
You have to get used to these things.

574
00:43:02,380 --> 00:43:05,616
You're my fiancÃ©e. Why shouldn't you
get used to these things then?

575
00:43:05,683 --> 00:43:07,718
Because I want to be alone.

576
00:43:09,153 --> 00:43:10,555
What exactly is going on, Yesha?

577
00:43:12,090 --> 00:43:13,157
Nothing.

578
00:43:14,525 --> 00:43:15,893
Don't bother me, okay?

579
00:43:16,794 --> 00:43:19,063
I just want to know why you're unhappy.

580
00:43:19,130 --> 00:43:21,365
I'm not.

581
00:43:21,432 --> 00:43:22,500
Yesha.

582
00:43:23,367 --> 00:43:24,235
Ah Si.

583
00:43:27,905 --> 00:43:30,041
Yesha has been busy the whole day.

584
00:43:30,408 --> 00:43:33,044
She probably couldn't sleep last night
because she was too nervous.

585
00:43:33,978 --> 00:43:36,114
Let her get some rest.

586
00:43:38,449 --> 00:43:39,450
That's right.

587
00:43:40,551 --> 00:43:43,654
Do you want me to regret
our engagement on the very first day?

588
00:43:44,555 --> 00:43:45,623
Ah Si.

589
00:43:46,390 --> 00:43:49,293
If you don't learn
how to be a good husband

590
00:43:50,161 --> 00:43:53,664
and manage the company well,

591
00:43:54,532 --> 00:43:57,301
how can you make Yesha happy?

592
00:43:59,103 --> 00:44:01,172
When the time comes,

593
00:44:02,173 --> 00:44:04,242
I might not be able to keep

594
00:44:04,642 --> 00:44:08,146
a good daughter-in-law like Yesha
no matter how good I am.

595
00:44:10,681 --> 00:44:11,649
Exactly.

596
00:44:12,950 --> 00:44:14,452
Ah Si knows very well

597
00:44:15,353 --> 00:44:17,221
how bad my temper is.

598
00:44:18,756 --> 00:44:22,193
If people don't fulfill
their promises to me,

599
00:44:22,960 --> 00:44:24,795
I won't let them off easily.

600
00:44:25,463 --> 00:44:26,531
Right, Ah Si?

601
00:44:27,064 --> 00:44:28,199
Okay.

602
00:44:28,266 --> 00:44:31,335
I'll go and deal
with those reporters, okay?

603
00:44:51,756 --> 00:44:52,857
Yutian.

604
00:44:54,025 --> 00:44:55,526
Contact Shancai now.

605
